      "Mentored junior developers and conducted code reviews to ensure quality and adherence to best practices",
      "Implemented automated testing using Jest and Cypress, achieving 80% code coverage",
      "Collaborated with UI/UX designers to implement responsive and accessible interfaces"
    ],
    technologies: ["React", "Node.js", "TypeScript", "PostgreSQL", "Docker", "AWS"]
  },
  {
    role: "Full Stack Developer",
    company: "WebSolutions Inc",
    period: "March 2019 - December 2021",
